[{"id":"1a0f7ce99791c98ff2279941cf89b23a","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: ShopNBC Times and Viewing Details","date":"2008-03-25T13:08:41.000Z","formatted_date":"Mar 25, 2008","formatted_time":"1:08 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: RhodesVictor@aol.com [mailto:RhodesVictor@aol.com] \nSent: Friday, March 21, 2008 8:16 AM\nTo: RhodesVictor@aol.com; angelaferferi@yahoo.com\nSubject: ShopNBC Times and Viewing Details\n\n \n\nDear Friends\n\nPlease take the time out to watch us on ShopNBC and see the new\ncollection kits of StevenVictorMD Skincare. Also we are very excited to\nannounce that Emma Samms former star of General Hospital and Dynasty\nwill join in.  She is a fan and loves the StevenVIctorMD skincare line.\n\nWarmest Regards\n\n \n\nFor those in other countries you can go to TV.ShopNBC.com website and\ntype in Steven Victor MD SkinCare in the search box and watch the show\nlive on your computer.\n\n \n\nThe Times are as follows:\n\n \n\nShopNBC Show Times EST\n\n \n\nMonday 3/24\n\n4pm\n\n9pm\n\n \n\nTues 3/26\n\n7am\n\n1pm\n\n \n\nWed 3/27\n\n9am\n\n \n\nSteven Victor MD\nVictor Dermatology & Rejuvenation PC\n30 East 76th Street\nNew York, New York 10021\n212 249 3050\nFax 212 249 1482\nCell 917 459 8252\nOffice Website: www.stevenvictormdmedispa.com\n<http://www.stevenvictormdmedispa.com/> \nProduct Website: www.stevenvictormd.com <http://www.stevenvictormd.com/>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n________________________________\n\nCreate a Home Theater Like the Pros. Watch the video on AOL Home\n<http://home.aol.com/diy/home-improvement-eric-stromer?video=15?ncid=aol\nhom00030000000001> .\n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:x=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel\" xmlns:p=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:powerp